{"tid":1030192,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一食熱野打冷震之類全身痕到好似比針吉咁?","createTime":"2019-02-20T20:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T18:19:16.000Z","uid":183601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6264734fbabbcbdd13a56096e831f7670ee7591","tid":1030192,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:18:34.000Z","msg":"通常食熱嘅湯麵, 食辣麵, 著厚衫跑完一段路散唔到熱 (例如追車), 打冷震<br />\n由頭皮到個身就會好似有好撚多支針吉埋嚟咁撚痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會狂R 但唔會有用<br />\n屌那星近排唔知係咪天氣問題<br />\n可能有少少起雞皮之後就會狂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e819fd7b580e82dd7de2ed6f64f4f362f893d3","tid":1030192,"uid":109086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:29:58.000Z","msg":"我頂多都係熱果陣頭頂痕<br />\n巴打可能熱過敏 / 蕁麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836078015f63c1cf0e0cb47c00b752dfa784343e","tid":1030192,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e819fd7b580e82dd7de2ed6f64f4f362f893d3","tid":1030192,"uid":109086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:29:58.000Z","msg":"我頂多都係熱果陣頭頂痕<br />\n巴打可能熱過敏 / 蕁麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:37:59.000Z","msg":"蕁麻疹就應該唔係<br />\n因為痕嘅位唔會有&quot;欄&quot;<br />\n但熱過敏係咩嚟??"},{"pid":"abe5f3360d58d962cfce78543688a1d9b3a7f3b6","tid":1030192,"uid":97776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:45:03.000Z","msg":"有時熱嗰陣個頭勁痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0534c1114188d1bcd83272cb086711fea175c7","tid":1030192,"uid":48084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:46:07.000Z","msg":"痕左5-6年，冇咩大變化<br />\n唯一幫助到嘅就係保持心境平靜<br />\n只要身體溫度升得太快就會痕到仆街<br />\n同一定要著可以除嘅外套，一痕就除左佢，降左溫就冇事<br />\n其實運動出汗有用，不過懶做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7d0ae2e0a5d4ed58defe8b05128cea1090ac2a","tid":1030192,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:08:47.000Z","msg":"頂多出汗會痕<br />\n打冷震又無咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201243d96c686a510f0061d67f5ff82cb0d039a7","tid":1030192,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:30:41.000Z","msg":"我係乾燥先會出現呢個情況<br />\n例如沖完涼入冷氣房幾個鐘 出去返去曬到太陽/出汗之類就會咁"},{"pid":"9bedb5e67ff0db79bc4c9f33ec3d584edc0a070a","tid":1030192,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:32:38.000Z","msg":"月經post, 冇解決方法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd36ce51565bcd261104335b69ae3404ff7534a6","tid":1030192,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:38:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會平時環境太污糟引致？<br />\n我以前冇呢個問題，上年做左地盤就一熱身痕，而家辭左工就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0582dd1307df95f3b25237739781157ab54797","tid":1030192,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:48:45.000Z","msg":"有，總之冬天一熱但又未熱到出汗都會，成身都痕到仆街，但一出汗就冇事，做運動有助減少呢個情況出現。"},{"pid":"8e7c4d14ad9e1d320d828de8194f4166b6f70632","tid":1030192,"uid":199970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T21:54:01.000Z","msg":"通常11月開始到3,4月 有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我高中開始發 表面乜野都冇 冇紅冇粒粒冇盛 好似內裡皮下面痕咁 <br />\n多數會係面側 頸 下爬兩側 上背上胸 最常一定頭皮！！！<br />\n年年一發都睇過research 似係膽囊性蕁蔴疹 冇得點醫嫁<br />\n生活正常健康個排就冇事 e.g.作息正常 常運動 我記得高中個陣有一排特登咁做就冇事 之後冇keep到依家 都叫痕到咁打呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a827d0d36cf380b0375c90f0558dc8628ef2c8c","tid":1030192,"uid":199970,"like":0,"dislike":