\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931844bee40a94774b5447d64207f232832d22c6","tid":1030192,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:18:10.000Z","msg":"有時係突然之間比針拮一下 ，跟住feel到頭頂好似出緊煙咁"},{"pid":"6834261633ee82a21d6e41ff519e0b99f05b09a6","tid":1030192,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:21:02.000Z","msg":"深呼吸再令到個降溫非常之有幫助。"},{"pid":"0c3324fb0ccbb391bb1700b28b8619c93f4d830b","tid":1030192,"uid":114148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:56:05.000Z","msg":"真係好撚煩 做運動又會痕唔敢做 係到死循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ada3d4f8cf5e169c7b604695028193ecbd23f0f","tid":1030192,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"我以前都有咁情況<br />\n一熱就俾針拮同會成身紅色一撻撻<br />\n<br />\n做運動出返汗就會冇"},{"pid":"a3ffd1bbf53cd3bb5cafdde5b3e11c483483b190","tid":1030192,"uid":27978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:26:31.000Z","msg":"好似沖涼唔好沖太熱"},{"pid":"96a2f3b1edf297eea82d59625e1f3825c4864d73","tid":1030192,"uid":193476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"認真，要去做劇烈運動，出一身汗，一兩次之後就會無事。<br />\n<br />\n經過我多年經驗，我覺得係冬天少運動同出汗，皮膚失去彈性，一遇熱肌肉膨漲，皮膚一時跟唔上就有輕微撕列，做成拮拮痕。查Cream保濕嗰啲係完全無用。只有保持隔日做運動先可以解決。"},{"pid":"9b63451cc0b359efea79e470ef4b50c012041034","tid":1030192,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"綜合咁多位巴絲意見, 試下做返運動先<br />\n本身都有做開運動, 不過呢個冬天懶咗, 做得好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 幾粒鐘前打邊爐, 一食第一舊肉即刻痕, 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要即刻隊半罐可樂先無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}